data.description: Incredible Craftsman style home on over an acre with no HOA!  Beautiful views in many directions will keep you outside to enjoy the cool mountain air. Inside this 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home will make sure you are comfortable with extra large rooms and spacious bathrooms and closets. This open and split floor plan home has been built with low maintenance and high quality in mind, allowing you to enjoy your home not work on it!  Recently installed metal roof and metal wrapped facia will give you years of worry free protection.  The oversized 2 car garage / work shop will let you take on any project with room to spare. Covered front and rear patio space with even more patio out back. Full hook up Rv parking with 50 amp service. Separate utility room as well. Come see Today!
